{"tid":2173690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"830 著白衫！ 830著白衫！ 830著白衫！","createTime":"2020-08-25T11:28:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-25T11:40:29.000Z","uid":135891,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0ef001f7a44d582fd78d5ba3f93918ac33168fe0","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:28:19.000Z","msg":"<p class=\"center\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">8月30號 - 香港重光日</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">香港民族嘅重要日子</span></p><br />\n<br />\n1945年8月30號 大家熟悉嘅夏慤少將帶領英國皇家海軍艦隊抵達維多利亞港 宣吿<span class=\"gold\">香港重光</span> <br />\n香港人重獲自由<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望大家果日可以一齊著白色素服<br />\n<span class=\"x-large\">素服：係向香港保衛戰中犧牲嘅軍人致敬<br />\n白色：係象徵對香港再次重光嘅盼望</span>"},{"pid":"7c245be63a35eff2bfd091fd19dbcaa78ee54a71","tid":2173690,"uid":278184,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},{"pid":"1ee2b632d9d7748df001c0bccd5e76f21cdcf531","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"7c245be63a35eff2bfd091fd19dbcaa78ee54a71","tid":2173690,"uid":278184,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:31:40.000Z","msg":"九唔搭八"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:34:26.000Z","msg":"重光紀念日係一個比港共刪除嘅日子 但對香港係極有意義"},{"pid":"65016147c304cbd211b56fec7cd90dbcbe48b0b1","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:37:47.000Z","msg":"民族自強 香港獨立"},{"pid":"3e278c72a30da7cf53289a8d3b9ecd4e2e089d07","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:38:07.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"0fef0ad6980fa7e3f4d242749c4d4a5ecde0572e","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:38:18.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"239761ca592f4f933e89a7d61857ffba366bde96","tid":2173690,"uid":135891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-25T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pi